# portal-maven-nexus â€” Private Maven Repository @ maven.slytechs.com

One-command, fully containerized, auto-HTTPS private Maven repository using:
- Sonatype Nexus Repository OSS 3
- Traefik v3 with automatic Let's Encrypt certificates
- Zero-downtime, production-grade

## Quick start (on any Linux colo/DC server)

```bash
cd /opt
sudo mkdir portal-maven-nexus && cd portal-maven-nexus
sudo curl -L https://raw.githubusercontent.com/slytechs-repos/portal-maven-nexus/main/docker-compose.yml -o docker-compose.yml
sudo docker compose up -d